[[The Haunted Pantry]] is one of the first open adventuring areas in the game. The Haunted Pantry is ideal for newcomers to begin leveling their characters. And for stalking asparagus.

The Haunted Pantry is initially located directly on the [[Right Side of the Tracks]] main map, but after the [[The Manor in Which You're Accustomed|door to the manor]] is found, it becomes one of the interior rooms of the [[Spookyraven Manor]], which replaces the pantry on the Right Side of the Tracks map.
